content.query:
SELECT [Nome Órgão Superior],[Nome Contratado], [Valor Final Compra], [Valor Inicial Compra]
,(CAST(REPLACE([Valor Final Compra],',','.') as DECIMAL(20,4)) - CAST(REPLACE([Valor Inicial Compra],',','.') as DECIMAL(20,4)))  as DIF
 FROM [dbo].[202301_Compras]
 GROUP BY [Nome Órgão Superior],[Nome Contratado], [Valor Final Compra], [Valor Inicial Compra]
 HAVING (CAST(REPLACE([Valor Final Compra],',','.') as DECIMAL(20,4)) - CAST(REPLACE([Valor Inicial Compra],',','.') as DECIMAL(20,4))) > 0
 ORDER BY [Nome Órgão Superior],DIF DESC
